    "description": "<strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏现已开启抢先体验！</h2></strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>3章线性主线剧情，以及30个主线关卡<br></li><li>10个不同的可用角色<br></li><li>26个各具特色的大型天赋点所编织出来的天赋树系统<br></li><li>超过百个不同属性加成的词条，搭配上等阶组成的芯片系统<br></li><li>还有30关更加具有挑战性的自由挑战关卡</li></ul>吐槽，游戏BUG，意见反馈群：601171601<br><strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏简介</h2></strong><br>《尘埃之谜》是一款融合有<strong>塔防策略要素</strong>的<strong>RPG</strong>游戏。<br>玩家将扮演一名叫做“莉夏.可莫”的少女，她被卷入了一场席卷全城的“智能机械叛乱”。<br>在她求生无望时，却被赋予了强大的，名叫“<strong>记忆体</strong>”的力量，让她得以利用过去战争中留存下来的“英雄记忆”进行战斗。<br>并且，由于她自身的特殊性，也被要求和其他人一同组成小队，来解决这场机械叛乱危机，并逐渐深入追查背后的源头。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>游戏特点</strong></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >2D塔防战斗</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1656840/extras/5e5b389deb5b611b26bb274eef6d4de9.poster.avif?t=1720778411\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1656840/extras/5e5b389deb5b611b26bb274eef6d4de9.webm?t=1720778411\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1656840/extras/5e5b389deb5b611b26bb274eef6d4de9.mp4?t=1720778411\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>沙漠，工厂，夜晚，白天……<br>面对各种各样的敌人，利用手上的记忆体<br>依靠策略或是配装，将其击溃！<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >各具特色的记忆体</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1656840/extras/dce386286674a1d0945307532e51217a.poster.avif?t=1720778411\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1656840/extras/dce386286674a1d0945307532e51217a.webm?t=1720778411\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1656840/extras/dce386286674a1d0945307532e51217a.mp4?t=1720778411\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>10名分工不同的可用记忆体，每个记忆体带有一个专属技能<br>了解她们的用途，并组成相互连携的队伍！<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >芯片配装</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1656840/extras/fd137cc46dc59b42bd2c41a447f3d104.poster.avif?t=1720778411\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1656840/extras/fd137cc46dc59b42bd2c41a447f3d104.webm?t=1720778411\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1656840/extras/fd137cc46dc59b42bd2c41a447f3d104.mp4?t=1720778411\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>超过百个词条组装而成的芯片系统<br>能对记忆体的每一个属性进行加成<br>还有独特的套装芯片效果，能彻底改变记忆体的作战方式<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >天赋系统</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1656840/extras/7adb1b7ed1a5914b65be226e13efd072.poster.avif?t=1720778411\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1656840/extras/7adb1b7ed1a5914b65be226e13efd072.webm?t=1720778411\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1656840/extras/7adb1b7ed1a5914b65be226e13efd072.mp4?t=1720778411\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>一张完整的大型天赋树，根据玩家的选择来进行取舍<br>不论是加强长板，还是补齐短板，都能自由选择<br>针对玩家自己的队伍，让天赋点成为你的助力<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >挑战关卡</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1656840/extras/32dfdc57111906cbe2d0cb9c195cfe5b.poster.avif?t=1720778411\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1656840/extras/32dfdc57111906cbe2d0cb9c195cfe5b.webm?t=1720778411\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1656840/extras/32dfdc57111906cbe2d0cb9c195cfe5b.mp4?t=1720778411\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>按照难度分级划定的自由挑战关<br>给予玩家挑战的同时，也能通过其中获取额外的回报<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >线性剧情</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1656840/extras/3052d4e01e43886aaab9bbb741149d68.poster.avif?t=1720778411\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1656840/extras/3052d4e01e43886aaab9bbb741149d68.webm?t=1720778411\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1656840/extras/3052d4e01e43886aaab9bbb741149d68.mp4?t=1720778411\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>跟随莉夏的脚步，见证她的旅程<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >角色介绍</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1656840/extras/ba00bac21769398a04b76ecf4fa22c14.avif?t=1720778411\" width=600 height=1720 /></span>",
